#SummerHairCare #ScalpCare #FrizzFreeHair #HairGoals #haircare #summerhaircare #beauty 🧿

Just because it’s trending… doesn’t mean I’m buying it 💅🏽
Here’s a list of things I’m no longer falling for — from useless gadgets to outdated gender norms!

📌 Matcha? Overrated.
📌 Dyson Airwrap for fine hair? Not worth the hype.
📌 Collagen on your skin? Science says no thanks.
📌 10-step skincare? My skin needs care, not chaos.
📌 First copies? That’s disrespecting the designer and the design.
📌 “Be polite, quiet, and likable”? I’ll be real, thanks.
📌 Cook, birth, behave? I’m not society’s puppet.

If it doesn’t serve me, I’m not subscribing. Period.

✨ Which one are you done falling for?
